OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781262183
OL,3,CDevon councillors considering legal
OL,4,Caction over ongoing water quality
OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,FDevon County Council is looking into
OL,8,Fwhether it could take legal action, to
OL,9,Fensure the county's water is safe and
OL,10,Freliable, after being "let down" by
OL,11,Fauthorities.
OL,13,FIt says it wants to see if it can
OL,14,Flawfully play a role alongside
OL,15,Fnational regulators to support the
OL,16,Fprotection of public health and the
OL,17,Fenvironment.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781262183
OL,3,CDevon councillors considering legal
OL,4,Caction over ongoing water quality
OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,FThe announcement follows water
OL,8,Fconcerns, including 2024's
OL,9,Fcryptosporidium outbreak in Brixham
OL,10,Fand a number of sewage discharges
OL,11,Facross the county.
OL,13,FThe Government, the Environment Agency
OL,14,Fand the water regulator have been
OL,15,Fcontacted for comment.
OL,17,FSouth West Water says it's investing
OL,18,Fmillions of pounds to improve water
OL,19,Fquality and says the latest data shows
OL,20,Fits plan is working, although it
OL,21,Facknowledges more needs to be done.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781262183
OL,3,CDevon councillors considering legal
OL,4,Caction over ongoing water quality
OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,FThe company was fined #1.9million
OL,8,Fafter admitting supplying water that
OL,9,Fwas unfit for human consumption in
OL,10,FSouth Devon.
OL,12,FA total of 537 people were left unwell
OL,13,Fand 10 were taken to hospital after
OL,14,Fthe water supply was contaminated with
OL,15,Fthe parasite cryptosporidium in
OL,16,FBrixham in May 2024.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781262183
OL,3,CDevon councillors considering legal
OL,4,Caction over ongoing water quality
OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,FAround 16,000 homes and businesses in
OL,8,FBrixham, Kingswear and Paignton - a
OL,9,Fpopulation of almost 39,000 people -
OL,10,Fwere told to boil their water. The
OL,11,Fnotice was not lifted until July 2024.
OL,13,FCouncil leader Julian Brazil told ITV
OL,14,FNews West Country: "We feel very let
OL,15,Fdown by government and Westminster, by
OL,16,Fthe regulator and by the Environment
OL,17,FAgency and of course the water company.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781262183
OL,3,CDevon councillors considering legal
OL,4,Caction over ongoing water quality
OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,F"So rather than just sit back and do
OL,8,Fnothing, we feel we've got to step up
OL,9,Fand try and make sure the people of
OL,10,FDevon are listened to."
OL,12,FIn a statement, he added: "Enough is
OL,13,Fenough. We have been let down for too
OL,14,Flong.
OL,26,@tD@[OU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781262183
OL,3,CDevon councillors considering legal
OL,4,Caction over ongoing water quality
OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,F"Residents rightly expect safe and
OL,8,Freliable water services. We are
OL,9,Fcarefully considering what role, if
OL,10,Fany, the council can lawfully play
OL,11,Falongside national regulators to
OL,12,Fsupport the protection of public
OL,13,Fhealth and the environment.
OL,15,F"The only way to ensure water company
OL,16,Fexecutives act is to hit them in the
OL,17,Fpocket by attaching a surcharge for
OL,18,Ffines to their already inflated
OL,19,Fsalaries and bonuses.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781262183
OL,3,CDevon councillors considering legal
OL,4,Caction over ongoing water quality
OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,F"Executives should also be subject to
OL,8,Fthe full force of the law.
OL,10,F"Any action would be subject to
OL,11,Fdetailed legal advice and the
OL,12,Fevidential thresholds required for
OL,13,Fformal proceedings. The council will
OL,14,Fcontinue to work constructively with
OL,15,Fpartners while ensuring that
OL,16,Fresidents' concerns are properly
OL,17,Faddressed."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781262183
OL,3,CDevon councillors considering legal
OL,4,Caction over ongoing water quality
OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,FA South West Water spokesperson told
OL,8,FITV News: "We recognise concerns about
OL,9,Fwater quality in Devon and we continue
OL,10,Fto work proactively with councils to
OL,11,Fdiscuss our local plans and deliver
OL,12,Fimprovements.
OL,14,F"We're investing #760 million to
OL,15,Ftackle storm overflows and have
OL,16,Freduced spills by 17% in the last
OL,17,Fyear, with spill duration down by 25%.
OL,18,FWe know there is more to do but the
OL,19,Fdata shows the plan is working.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781262183
OL,3,CDevon councillors considering legal
OL,4,Caction over ongoing water quality
OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,F"We are looking forward to the
OL,8,Fopportunity to discuss our multi-
OL,9,Fmillion-pound plans to improve water
OL,10,Fquality at Devon County Council's
OL,11,Fwater summit. We appreciate the
OL,12,Fopportunity to help shape the event
OL,13,Fand continue to engage constructively
OL,14,Fwith the council."
OL,16,FThe council will also host Devon's
OL,17,Ffirst Water Quality Summit this autumn.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781262183
OL,3,CDevon councillors considering legal
OL,4,Caction over ongoing water quality
OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,FLed by the council's deputy leader,
OL,8,FPaul Arnott, the summit will bring
OL,9,Ftogether regulators, water companies,
OL,10,Fdistrict councils, landowners,
OL,11,Fcommunity groups and other
OL,12,Fstakeholders involved in protecting
OL,13,Fand improving Devon's rivers, streams,
OL,14,Festuaries and coastal waters.
OL,16,FThe council says that only around a
OL,17,Ffifth of Devon's surface water bodies
OL,18,Fcurrently meet the "good ecological
OL,19,Fstatus" required under national
OL,20,Fregulations.
OL,26,@zD@TOU{D@GO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781262183
OL,3,CDevon councillors considering legal
OL,4,Caction over ongoing water quality
OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,FKey pressures include agricultural
OL,8,Frunoff, urban pollution, wastewater
OL,9,Fdischarges and the impacts of climate
OL,10,Fchange on rainfall and flooding.
OL,12,FMr Arnott said: "Water quality is
OL,13,Frightly a matter of strong public
OL,14,Fconcern. Residents should have
OL,15,Fconfidence in the safety of their
OL,16,Fwater and in the protection of the
OL,17,Fnatural environment.
OL,26,@tD@QOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781262183
OL,3,CDevon councillors considering legal
OL,4,Caction over ongoing water quality
OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,F"The summit will provide an
OL,8,Fopportunity for open and constructive
OL,9,Fdialogue between all relevant
OL,10,Forganisations, including expectations
OL,11,Faround investment, infrastructure and
OL,12,Fenvironmental performance."
OL,14,FSome local authorities have taken
OL,15,Flegal action against water companies
OL,16,Fin specific circumstances, including
OL,17,Fthe use of s222 of the Local
OL,18,FGovernment Act 1972.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@[O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
