CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781262183
OL,3,CDevon councillors considering legal
OL,4,Caction over ongoing water quality
OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,FThe council says it's currently
OL,8,Fconsidering all its options and how to
OL,9,Fbest serve and protect its residents
OL,10,Fand communities.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
